kabasuji.model

Class Level

  • java.lang.Object
    • kabasuji.model.Level
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    LightningLevel, PuzzleLevel, ReleaseLevel

    public abstract class Level
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class is an abstract model class for the levels. It contains the shared logic for the different types of the levels like Puzzle, Lightning and Release.
    Author:
    Ethan

    Serialized Form
